This is a game for guessing a number:
.The Number shall be between 1 and 100
.The player may choose the difficulty Easy or Hard
.The player is informed if the guess is correct or not and if the guess is higher or lower than the target
.The number of lives is reduced for a failed attempt
.The player is informaed if they get it right
.The player is informed if they do not get the number in time
